items.title: Awesome Ios
items.content_text:
### ScrollView

*   [SpreadsheetView (‚≠ê3.5k)](https://github.com/bannzai/SpreadsheetView) - Full configurable spreadsheet view user interfaces for iOS applications. With this framework, you can easily create complex layouts like schedule, Gantt chart or timetable as if you are using Excel.
